{
  "stem": "8.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, I remember the secrecy, how we tried to hide them and protect them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, often they went on during the night and escaped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One night, we had a rabbi who lost 11 children who came to, to stay with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He lost his children few years back and he remarried in our back yard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the middle of the night they married him with a woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know where and I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, let me tell you, we had a two-room apartment, plus our, our restaurant, plus kitchen and an entry hall, which was like another room.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, we had about five families staying with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those were staying with us all the time, as well as some families who came, or individuals who came, and then left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The families who stayed with us were somewhat related to us, like distant relatives.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think they had a choice who, who would come to live with us, and who we'd, we'd want to invite.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, they brought in food with them so that we actually were better fed when they were there than before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, this family that moved in, they were well-to-do and they had five little children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, they brought butter and I remember seeing the mother giving bread and butter to the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How I would have liked to have a piece, but of course, I wouldn't ask for it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at this time, my father was still there, but my younger brother, my parents decided to send to Edeleny to be with my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because, he was very fragile and very young, and we decided that he would have more food there, so he left.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
